      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Turning back the clock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.19999999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ開催前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day before the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（マズい……さっきまでポケットにあったのに）\n（財布がない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Holly molly… Where’s my wallet?)\n(It was in my pocket just a moment ago.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2033.3333333333333,
          "startTime": 11.966666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n星見プロの{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚\nHoshimi Productions' {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あっおはようございます、天動さん\n今日はレッスンですか？　うちの子達もなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good morning‚ Tendo-san.\nAre you here for a lesson‚ like our girls?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 21.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね\n私達もこれからスタジオに向かいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nWe’re going to the studio now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.544979887083173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 26.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、あの……\nもしかして何か困っていますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…hmm…\nIs something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.57627449184656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 31.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "先ほどから\nキョロキョロしているようですけど……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been looking\naround the place anxiously…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、実は財布を落としたみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ er‚ I can’t find my wallet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 38.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nでしたら私も探すので、来た道を戻りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nI’ll help. Let’s backtrack along the way that you came.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.30356063842773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え、天動さんが？　そんな、悪いですよ\nそれに、天動さんはレッスンがあるでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Tendo-san? I’d feel bad involving you.\nBesides‚ you have a lesson to go to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.02079174108803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 51.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それぐらい構いませんよ。遅刻した理由を\n説明すれば、みんな分かってくれますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not a problem.\nThe others will understand if there’s a proper reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.180352225899696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 58.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、今ここで困っている\n{user}さんを見捨てたりしたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything‚\nIf I abandoned {user}-san when you need help‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれに怒られちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu and Sumire would be mad at me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 64.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "あの子達がここにいたら\nきっと同じようにお手伝いするはずですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They would be helping out too‚\nif they were here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、財布の中には免許証やクレジットカードなど\n大切なものが入っているんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ you have important things in your wallet\nlike your driver’s license and credit card‚ don’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.44160313531756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 76.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女は若手で一、二を争う人気グループのセンターだ）\n（俺の落とし物なんかで手を借りる訳にはいかない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Tendo-san is the center of one of the brightest up-and-coming groups.)\n(I can’t ask her to help me find my wallet.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2333333350718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 83.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あっ、天動さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ Tendo-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいって言ってるのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to do this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 88.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、結構頑固なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re a stubborn one‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 91.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、気にしないで下さい\n私が勝手にやっていることですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there’s no need for you to worry.\nI chose to do this on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.07258018478751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 95.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら君の方こそ頑固なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like you’re the stubborn one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 99.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ私は{user}さんほどでは\nないですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Not as much as you are‚\n{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 104.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、それじゃあ一緒にお財布を探しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let’s go look for this wallet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 107.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（その前に、天動さんがレッスンに遅れる旨を）\n（スタジオに連絡しておいた方がいいだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Before we do that‚ we should contact the studio)\n(and let them know that Tendo-san would be late.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（カバンの中に入っている携帯電話を漁り）\n（そこで、存在するはずのないものを発見してしまった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I search in my bag for my cell phone)\n(and find something that should not have been there.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha",
      "startTime": 120.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_01-rui015.m4a",
